Events at East Bay Country Club Rest
Our complete party, wedding package includes all staff, linen, center piece, dance floor and utilities. We have a newly renovated Gazebo and two banquet rooms.  All rooms have floor to ceiling glass overlooking our lakes, as well as their own dance floors, bars and restrooms. East Bay Country Club Rest/Clubhouse hosts every special occasion including weddings, anniversaries, prom parties, birthday parties and many more.

About Us
Located on the beautiful west central coast of Florida in Largo, East Bay Golf Club is one of the most popular public layouts in Pinellas County and the Tampa Bay area.
East Bay offers a championship 18 hole par-71 layout, practice range, putting greens, pro shop, clubhouse and Pro Shot GPS yardage system on the entire 90-cart fleet.
